### Backend

#### [NEW] [server/src/services/auth.service.js](file:///Users/danielkalo/Documents/CS%207180%20-%20Vibe%20Coding%20%28Python%29/Project%202%20-%20Collective%20Unconscious/server/src/services/auth.service.js)
- `findOrCreateUser(googleProfile)` — upsert User by googleId
- `generateTokens(userId)` — returns `{ accessToken, refreshToken }` (JWT access: 15m, refresh: 7d)
- `rotateRefreshToken(oldToken)` — validates old refresh token, issues new pair (rotation strategy)
- `revokeRefreshToken(token)` — deletes from DB on logout

#### [NEW] [server/src/config/passport.js](file:///Users/danielkalo/Documents/CS%207180%20-%20Vibe%20Coding%20%28Python%29/Project%202%20-%20Collective%20Unconscious/server/src/config/passport.js)
- Configure `passport-google-oauth20` Strategy
- On success: call `findOrCreateUser`, then issue JWT pair and set cookies

#### [NEW] [server/src/controllers/auth.controller.js](file:///Users/danielkalo/Documents/CS%207180%20-%20Vibe%20Coding%20%28Python%29/Project%202%20-%20Collective%20Unconscious/server/src/controllers/auth.controller.js)
- `redirectToGoogle` — initiates OAuth flow
- `googleCallback` — handles callback, sets `accessToken` + `refreshToken` cookies, redirects to `/`
- `refreshToken` — validates refresh token, returns new access token
- `logout` — revokes refresh token, clears cookies
- `getMe` — returns current user (from JWT), strips sensitive fields

#### [NEW] [server/src/controllers/users.controller.js](file:///Users/danielkalo/Documents/CS%207180%20-%20Vibe%20Coding%20%28Python%29/Project%202%20-%20Collective%20Unconscious/server/src/controllers/users.controller.js)
- `getProfile(userId)` — returns public profile + participation history (logs they've written in)
- `updateProfile(userId, { displayName, bio })` — updates own profile

#### [NEW] [server/src/routes/auth.routes.js](file:///Users/danielkalo/Documents/CS%207180%20-%20Vibe%20Coding%20%28Python%29/Project%202%20-%20Collective%20Unconscious/server/src/routes/auth.routes.js)
